1
00:00:01,666 --> 00:00:05,157
This is a photograph of our village.
这是我们村庄的一张照片.

2
00:00:05,709 --> 00:00:08,130
Our village is in a valley.
我们的村庄坐落在一个山谷之中.

3
00:00:09,048 --> 00:00:11,250
It is between two hills.
它位于两座小山之间.

4
00:00:12,136 --> 00:00:14,341
The village is on a river.
它靠近一条小河.

5
00:00:16,047 --> 00:00:19,981
Here is another photograph of the village.
这是我们村庄的另一张照片.

6
00:00:21,431 --> 00:00:26,974
My wife and I are walking along the banks of the river.
我和妻子正沿河岸走着.

7
00:00:27,939 --> 00:00:29,669
We are on the left.
我们在河的左侧.

8
00:00:30,684 --> 00:00:32,762
There is a boy in the water.
河里面有个男孩.

9
00:00:33,744 --> 00:00:36,345
He is swimming across the river.
他正横渡小河.

10
00:00:37,105 --> 00:00:39,192
Here is another photograph.
这是另一张照片.

11
00:00:40,026 --> 00:00:41,731
This is the school building.
这是学校大楼.

12
00:00:42,788 --> 00:00:44,881
It is beside a park.
它位于公园的旁边.

13
00:00:45,876 --> 00:00:47,959
The park is on the right.
公园在右面.

14
00:00:49,522 --> 00:00:53,084
Some children are coming out of the building.
一些孩子正从楼里出来.

15
00:00:53,659 --> 00:00:56,874
Some of them are going into the park.
他们中有几个正走进公园.

